{"tid":903604,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不論男女，只要係家中排行最細，父母就會偏心哂佢，認唔認同？","createTime":"2018-11-15T16:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T01:24:12.000Z","uid":6097,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8334e42be896b54e99f9846ac68c70379ff0648e","tid":903604,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n家中有一弟<br />\n由細到大 我媽咪偏心佢偏到出面<br />\n只要我哋嗌交 就算佢錯 我都係畀人閙嗰個<br />\n話我無氣度、EQ底 、小事化大 、搞事<br />\n我相信好大做大嘅 都明嗰下幾感受<br />\n大家同一條腸出 點解唔可以公平啲<br />\n但相反 如果個細投訴你<br />\n佢就會出面幫口 但明明唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後無論你做咩 做得幾好 就算由細到大都畀外人讚<br />\n佢哋都覺得因爲你係大 要做榜樣 所以通通都係應份<br />\n但當個細做得比正常好少少 就讚到天上有地下無<br />\n又買嘢獎佢又放上FB曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲媽咪係鐘意自願做呀四<br />\n喺間房打機？又送湯又送茶 爭在未切埋生果<br />\n打到天光先瞓覺 叫工人唔好吸佢房住<br />\n連走廊都唔好吸 怕佢瞓得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我對貓毛敏感 家有五貓 可想而知如果唔吸嘅話我會有幾辛苦<br />\n咁我通宵做project呢？<br />\n由晏就四點做到夜晚四點<br />\n都係個工人自動自覺送飯餸入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要一大朝就畀吸塵機嘈醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n父母永遠覺得最細嗰個係唔識照顧自己<br />\n然後覺得最大嗰個應該連鋪電線都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最令我難受嘅係<br />\n佢好唔鐘意入佢間房<br />\n就算急到瀬 都唔準入佢間房個廁所<br />\n但個細直情可以入佢房飲可樂打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係未問過我就嚟拎走我間房個ps4<br />\n就係滿足佢同啲朋友「面對面」打<br />\n仲想借埋畀人 好彩我返得及時 咪已經無撚咗<br />\n但又唔借自己嗰部㗎喎 慷他人之慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我咪set密碼囉 之後畀媽咪話返我小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔就唔好打咁多機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心我就斯文啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之無論你做啲咪 啲父母都真係唔會企你角度諗<br />\n只要你只係維護自己嘅利益<br />\n佢就會話你唔讓個細 唔識體諒<br />\n然後仲覺得自己好公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好多朋友都係做人家姐 <br />\n大家講起偏心就有感而發 滔滔不絕<br />\n而啲呀妹都係會認自己係好明顯被偏心嗰個<br />\n<br />\n究竟點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸返先 但我同我細佬感情正常"},{"pid":"c7a9d79f5c352bbe8dc0260b386f29b3d9c29b94","tid":903604,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77794290314e1c5395657889fd8c9a2c3f0347b5","tid":903604,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7306ed0dff23bec19f45123993c8177e432831dd","tid":903604,"uid":17947,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"應該係關你係女事"},{"pid":"2f96899c079f973bfde357b6cacce9073ffd7042","tid":903604,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"有時會諗<br />\n如果當初得我一個...就好了<br />\n<br />\n我係兩邊親戚唯一嘅一個女<br />\n連理應鐘意仔嘅傳統四大長老<br />\n都係鐘意我多過細佬<br />\n<br />\n但偏偏自己屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abfe4c962800e22d76e04f157e443f2638db434","tid":903604,"uid":88782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"睇人嫁姐 我自己都係屋企最細 但屋企人都唔會話偏心<br />\n如果你係覺得咁難接受既 到下次佢地偏心咪發佢圍囉<br />\n你唔講心底果句出黎 情況唔會改善"},{"pid":"3163636527f010f28b2a8ca877037693b570aae6","tid":903604,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7306ed0dff23bec19f45123993c8177e432831dd","tid":903604,"uid":17947,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"應該係關你係女事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"我啲朋友做呀妹嘅<br />\n多數對上都係呀哥喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但佢哋嘅呀哥遇到嘅情況同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb2195f2d0f983b09846bc3e5d02e36ba7ee111","tid":903604,"uid":130298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"屋企排最細，但父母偏心阿哥，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844101cdbcfc16102d6c54e2a4e6c9aee38bfe55","tid":903604,"uid":17947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3163636527f010f28b2a8ca877037693b570aae6","tid":903604,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7306ed0dff23bec19f45123993c8177e432831dd","tid":903604,"uid":17947,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"應該係關你係女事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"我啲朋友做呀妹嘅<br />\n多數對上都係呀哥喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但佢哋嘅呀哥遇到嘅情況同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:37:47.000Z","msg":"你個細佬幾細呀"},{"pid":"31574a6ed67ef1ef40636f22db2dd2ec9b75267a","tid":903604,"uid":124256,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:40:08.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老母仲夠膽死話冇偏心過<br />\n屌佢縱撚到條友宜家皇帝咁款"},{"pid":"0a4d01eef23c73ff9428377b71c37e72f8bc4d96","tid":903604,"uid":220955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"唔同意"},{"pid":"8e994941ea6fef7f2ee81e